<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Landshut</head><p>Der Rat kündigt seinen Diener Marquart Waltmann wegen der in Landshut beschlagnahmten Waren Nürnberger Bürger an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_148" id="73v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l19">Der Stat cʒu Landſhut </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l20"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Als vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> vveiſheit vormals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l21">von <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan> hab <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> als den ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beẏ ew cʒu <expan>Landſh<ex>ut</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l22">
<del rend="strikethrough">ger </del> bekumert iſt <expan>woꝛde<ex>n</ex></expan> / Darümb <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> wir cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l23"><expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>Mark<ex>art</ex></expan> <expan>waltma<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> etc ut ın <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_148" id="73v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Landshut </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        weisheit vormals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan> hab
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, als den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bey ew czu
                            <expan>Landsh<ex>ut</ex></expan> bekumert ist
                            <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>, darümb <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>Mark<ex>art</ex></expan>
<expan>Waltma<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, etc. ut in
                        <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
